.global-nav-dropdown .global-nav__matrix { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; list-style: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; }
.global-nav-dropdown .global-nav__matrix-item { border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); flex: 1 1 auto; flex-wrap: wrap; margin: 0px; padding: 1rem; width: 33.33%; }
.global-nav-dropdown .global-nav__matrix-image { display: inline-block; height: auto; margin-bottom: 1rem; margin-right: 0.75rem; max-height: 2rem; max-width: 2rem; position: relative; top: 0.1rem; }
.global-nav-dropdown .global-nav__matrix-content { display: flex; flex: 1 1 auto; flex-direction: column; margin: 0px; padding-right: 1rem; width: 100%; }
.global-nav-dropdown .global-nav__inline-list .global-nav__list-item { display: inline; font-weight: 400; list-style: none; margin-right: 1.25rem; }
.global-nav-overlay { background-color: rgba(18, 18, 18, 0.4); height: 100%; left: 0px; margin: 0px; opacity: 0; pointer-events: none; position: fixed; top: 0px; width: 100%; z-index: 9; }
.skip-content a { color: rgb(0, 102, 204); display: block; left: -999px; position: absolute; top: -999px; }
.skip-content a:focus { background: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 1px solid rgb(0, 102, 204); left: 0px; padding: 3px; position: relative; top: 0px; z-index: 999999; }
